               <msContents>
                  <summary>fol. 4r-10v, 13r-94v Old Testament Books: Tobit, fol. 4r-10v, 13r-15v; Judith, fol. 16r-34r; Esther, fol. 34r-46v; 1 Esdras, fol. 48r-65r; Ezra, fol. 65r-76r; Nehemiah, fol. 76r-94v                    
                  </summary>
                  
                  
               </msContents>
