                  <handDesc><handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">Copied by ጽጌ (baptismal name ተክለ ፡ ወልድ), fol. 46v, with Tobit completed on 17 Ṭeqemt 1898 EC (27 October 1905 CE), fol. 15v, Judith completed on 30 Ṭeqemt 1898 EC (9 November 1905 CE), fol. 34r, and Esther completed in 1898 EC (1905/6 CE) in Dabra Moṭā, fol. 46v. Ezra 4:6-5:8, perhaps a rejected copy of fol. 68, fol. 95rv.
                     
                  </handNote></handDesc>
                  <additions><list><item xml:id="e1">	
                     Table of contents, fol. 3v. Leaves inserted into codex: fol. 11-12 is a bifolium from another contemporary manuscript containing Tobit 9:4-11:13 (fol. 11rv) and Judith 4:11-5:15 (fol. 12rv).</item><item xml:id="a1"><desc>Ownership note of Takla Wald (i.e. Ṣegē), fol. 94v</desc></item></list></additions>
                  <bindingDesc><decoNote xml:id="b1">Stamped leather over wood boards</decoNote></bindingDesc>
